---
---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#111111] relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Glow background effect -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3/4 h-3/4 bg-[var(--acento)]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <h2 class="titulo-seccion mb-16 text-center">Por qué <span>Elegirnos</span></h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="group bg-[#1a1a1a]/80 backdrop-blur-md p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[var(--acento)]/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(230,194,0,0.15)]">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-black/50 border border-[var(--acento)]/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:border-[var(--acento)]">
          <span class="text-[var(--acento)] text-2xl">✂️</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-white group-hover:text-[var(--acento)] transition-colors">Maestría</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-sans leading-relaxed">Barberos certificados con décadas de experiencia combinada perfeccionando cada detalle del corte clásico y moderno.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="group bg-[#1a1a1a]/80 backdrop-blur-md p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[var(--acento)]/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(230,194,0,0.15)]">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-black/50 border border-[var(--acento)]/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:border-[var(--acento)]">
          <span class="text-[var(--acento)] text-2xl">🕒</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-white group-hover:text-[var(--acento)] transition-colors">Puntualidad</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-sans leading-relaxed">Tu tiempo es oro. Garantizamos iniciar tu servicio exactamente a la hora agendada sin esperas innecesarias.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="group bg-[#1a1a1a]/80 backdrop-blur-md p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[var(--acento)]/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(230,194,0,0.15)]">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-black/50 border border-[var(--acento)]/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:border-[var(--acento)]">
          <span class="text-[var(--acento)] text-2xl">🥃</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-white group-hover:text-[var(--acento)] transition-colors">Bebidas</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-sans leading-relaxed">Disfruta de un whisky premium, café artesanal o cerveza fría por cortesía de la casa durante tu visita.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="group bg-[#1a1a1a]/80 backdrop-blur-md p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[var(--acento)]/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(230,194,0,0.15)]">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-black/50 border border-[var(--acento)]/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:border-[var(--acento)]">
          <span class="text-[var(--acento)] text-2xl">💎</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-white group-hover:text-[var(--acento)] transition-colors">Exclusividad</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-sans leading-relaxed">Un ambiente diseñado para el confort masculino, con sillones de cuero genuino y toallas calientes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
